<td data-valign="top" width="314"><p>Like a Digit of the Moon<br />
 In the Shadow of the Earth<br />
Spirit undergoeth Swoon<br />
 In the Vestibule of Birth:<br />
Dreameth transitory Trouble,<br />
 Weareth Hues of Heaven, hurled<br />
Hither, thither, as a Bubble<br />
 On the Ocean of the World.</p></td>
